detail.name: Sleepy Boy Technique
detail.effect: [Activate Main] Discard 1 card from your hand : Choose up to 2 Battle Cards with a total cost of 5 or less in your opponent's Battle Area and place them at the bottom of their owner's deck in any order.

detail.name: よいこ眠眠拳
detail.effect: 【起動 メイン】自分の手札1枚を捨てる：相手のバトルエリアのバトルカードをコストの合計が5以下になるように2枚までを選び、好きな順番でデッキの下に置く。
